snippet.title: DUELITE DEMO TRAILER: Experience the Wild West Card Roguelite! (July 15-28)
snippet.description:
🌵 Saddle up, partner! 🌵

Dive into the wild west with Duelite - the ultimate card-based roguelite adventure! 🃏🔥

🚀 Demo drops JULY 15-28!
🔖 Add us to your Steam wishlist now: DUELITE

Prepare for epic duels and legendary showdowns. Are you ready to duel? 🤠⚔️
